Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to my sea charts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fishmen" and "sea charts" this,\N"circumstances" that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about any of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm gonna destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Setting Out with a Smile!\NFarewell, Hometown Cocoyashi Village"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong Park has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:03:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're free!\N--Free!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Celebrate! Dance!\NArlong Park has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lived these\Npast eight years for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lived so we can smile today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna party 'til we drop,\Neven into tomorrow and the day after!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw Arlong Park for myself!\NIt's awesome! It's in pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The guy who did\Nthat must be really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?! The guy who\Nbeat Arlong is here, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?! Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy with the straw hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure he saved the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable as it may seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Is there any more meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like ol' Zoro's really hurtin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A normal person with those wounds\Nwould take two years to fully heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to take care of such\Na big injury on your own...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Are you folks really pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you even have... a ship doctor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doctor? That sounds good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy?\N--But a musician comes first. Right, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates sing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does that come first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Doctor. Where's Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't find her around,\Nthen she's probably "there."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're still here, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends've been\Nlooking for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Nojiko, Gen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Bellemere-san were alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you think she would\Nstop me from being a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she'd never let her\Nprecious daughter be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She wouldn't stop you!\N--Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would you really listen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Gen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are definitely\NBellemere's kids, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami. You've already\Nmade up your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then live how you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as your mother did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's what\NBellemere wants, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it's nice to only eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your wounds all better now, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This's nothin'! Some food\Nand drink'll fix it right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how long is this\Ndumb party gonna last?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the third day now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wanna celebrate,\Nyou should go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji! That melon you just had!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there something on it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the meat in your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure was. It's "raw ham melon,"\Nso there was raw ham on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raw ham melon?! That sounds yum!\NW-Where did you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole village is a buffet party,\Nso I dunno where I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been eating non-stop\Nfor three days straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. I'm done eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I think I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pick up some girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I am Captain Usopp...\N--Way to go, kiddo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--...hero of love and courage...\N--Can I have your autograph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who finished off the\Nstrongest fishman boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's an Usopp Support Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it? Who was it?\NWho beat the fishman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hmph. How boring.\N--What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be\Nmore down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.42,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "Why didn't this happen\Nbefore my dad died?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I felt at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm thinking about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been saved by that\Nstraw hat guy and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But starting tomorrow, we have\Nto start from scratch on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can forget\Nwhat's happened in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't think we need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I think what's most important\Nis what happens from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we do now.\NWhat things we need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who're gonna\Nsupport the villages now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to think that way instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cheeky kid!\N--Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you pinching me?!\NI don't understand! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was hoping to harass\Nyou some more for good measure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've harassed me plenty,\Nyou dumb tattoo punk girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Punk" will do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it come off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say, "No problem,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way to remove it fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be some scarring.\NThat's how tattoos are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know it's stupid of me.\NThey stay on for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... this tattoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even really Arlong's friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's like I've\Nbeen branded a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal! It's just a decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now me and you are the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tattoo I'd like to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two can dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's Usopp Support Song ♪185!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your daughters have grown up\Nto be truly strong and respectable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as if I'm\Nseeing you in life again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're going to be a marine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use trying\Nto stop me! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind's set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to live life\Nto its fullest from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost and sacrificed far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we're going to smile\Nas insanely much as possible now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raw ham melon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's no food around here.\NThat's no good. Time to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A grave? Did someone die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my deepest conveniences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Deepest concussions.\NHuh? Deepest compli--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deepest condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami is going to ride your ship.\NShe's going to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a dangerous journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. There's no way around that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you guys ever do anything\Nto take away Nami's smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will come kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm not gonna\Ntake it away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Support Song ♪368!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the coolest guy in the world!\NHis name is Great Captain Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:13:04.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm leaving this behind.\NThis belongs to all the villagers. --Nami."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Today's a big feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two know what today is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day I first met you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the day you two\Nbecame my daughters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm destroyed\Nthe orchard. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be strong girls who\Ncan smile even during hard times!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and then nice\Nthings will come to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll come, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Could you get me the salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you learned how to draw\Nsea charts, and now land maps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying navigation too now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigation, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is Nami's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:14:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use my navigation skills\Nto travel to all the world's oceans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'm gonna make a\Nworld map of everything I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your map of this island is your\Nfirst step toward your dream, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over, Bellemere-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took eight years,\Nbut we're finally free!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, and all the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you live through it,\Nnice things will come."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the villagers are smiling so happily\Nfrom the bottom of their hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And me! I'm thinking\Nof leaving this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really pleasant people,\Nand pretty strong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For eight years, I drew\Nlots of charts and maps...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this is the only one that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly it! This time,\NI'm going to draw charts for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to travel the world\Nwith them-- my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my dream, so... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not sure when I'll\Ncome back to this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:16:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This the last of it?\N--Yeah!\N--Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you finished loading it all?\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. We got lots of\Nprovisions now. We're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were only here a few days,\Nbut this island's full of memories, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe you a lot for\Neverything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get back to our\Nprofession of bounty-hunting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we look forward to the day\Nwe meet again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should get going, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on! What about Nami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You made another pass\Nat Nami-san again, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, you definitely did!\N--Oh, yeah. She achieved her goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can't stand that me and\NNami-san are all lovey-dovey!\N--and she has no reason to be a pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you an idiot?\N--What'd you call me?!\N--so she might be happier here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my happiness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Nami-san isn't on the boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then 98.72% of my reason\Nfor being on the boat is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! I couldn't find\Nthe raw ham melon anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's Nacchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing! Nobody's\Nseen her since this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She's leaving\Nall the money behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 100 million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left it in our house,\Nalong with a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's planning to journey\Nwithout her money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's the one who\Nrisked her life to earn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says it's okay, because\Nshe'll just steal some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once that girl says something,\Nthere's no changing her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool! We're the ones who\Nstill haven't thanked her enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami!\N--Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san!\N--Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the ship moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's started sprinting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says to get the ship moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's planning to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without letting us\Nthank her or say goodbye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can't be serious!\N--Set the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--H-Hey!\N--They're setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! We still haven't thanked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop, Nacchan!\N--At least let us thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I won't allow\Nyou to leave like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Is it okay to let her leave like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? It's her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? My wallet's gone!\N--Mine, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mine, too!\N--Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How dare you?!\N--You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. She hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows when she'll betray us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You lousy sneak thief!\N--Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give back our wallets!\N--You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come back anytime!\N--Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful to you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget our promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, everyone! I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got us good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My own little sister got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Genzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this scrap of paper, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool. She never learns.\NShe got another tattoo before she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What mark is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tangerine and a\Npinwheel, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Gen-san!\NWhat happened to your pinwheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt there's any need for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Gen-san!\NStay away from Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but, I want to see her smile, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She starts crying because\Nyou have such a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I supposed\Nto do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll make you laugh, right?!\NIf I always keep it here like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Nami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. I really don't think a dumb\Npinwheel is going to make Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. She laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no!\N--What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.38,0:24:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The newspaper's gone up in price!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What kind of problem is that?!\N--Then don't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying? We hafta\Nknow what's going on in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus we can use the backs\Nof the flyers as notepads!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! Good thinking!\N--See, like so!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bounty! Straw Hat Luffy\NBecomes Known to the World"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.53,0:24:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
